Package: PartRateDecomp
Title: Participation Rate Decomposition (Stan)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bayesian unobserved-components state-space model that decomposes
    the Australian labour-force participation rate into trend and cyclical
    components, jointly with log real GDP per capita and the unemployment
    rate. Replicates Evans, Moore & Rees (2018, RBA Bulletin) in Stan.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    posterior,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    readr,
    readxl,
    lubridate,
    httr,
    ggplot2,
    patchwork
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    cmdstanr (>= 0.7.0)
Remotes:
    stan-dev/cmdstanr
